<exploration xml:id="warm-actuemoslo-cenaFamiliar" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"> 

<title>Actúemoslo: Cena familiar</title>

<statement>
  <p>¿Cómo pueden mostrar los platos?</p>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Sample responses:</p>
<ul>
      <li>We can draw pictures of 8 plates.</li>
      <li>We can use 8 objects like counters to represent the flowers.</li>
      <li>We can write the number <q>8</q>.
      </li>
    </ul>
  </solution>


